     </tr>
     <tr>
       <td>[bots](https://github.com/orgs/hmcts/teams/bots) (super humans at HMCTS who have magical powers to do CI)</td>
       <td>admin</td>
     </tr>
    </table>

    `Note: You need to revoke the user level admin access you might have got while creating the repository.`
    
5. Add a branch protection rule for `master` branch with recommended settings
   - Enable `Require pull request reviews before merging`
   - Choose which status checks needs to be mandatory for merging PRs (this can be done only after checks like Jenkins are setup)
   - We recommend enabling `Include administrators`.